Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:35.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰的约会大作战 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 一 二 一 二 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是小兰喜欢的甜点 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰好幸福 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力圣岱 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起床啊 龙之介 会迟到哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起床 喂 龙之介 龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 起床啊 龙之介 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早 还无法进入情况 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒了吗 龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来吃早餐 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父代母职就是粗野了点 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么父代母职 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是男人相处有话好说嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事我从未听过 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌汤再一碗如何 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正在发育嘛 多吃点 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早还真温柔 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来 换衣服了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲我熬夜准备的 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 麻烦了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那花纹是父亲我亲手缝的 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心怀感激的去穿吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就找渣 有够胆的 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是必须要用蛮力让你穿了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 你在早餐下了药！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在味噌汤里加了一点点麻醉剂 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真龌龊！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲为你彻夜缝上了这花纹啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一举 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下情况对等了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on！Come on yo！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我个橡皮擦 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我个橡皮擦 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我个橡皮擦 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哪个呢？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那给我这个小猫咪 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我开这种玩笑 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫对等嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 不用管我 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流血了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 用这个 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 用这漂亮的手帕 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然穿着室内鞋 抄近路好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香的味道 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肥皂的味道吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来 她身上也有香味 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的手帕 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你很相配嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻子 不是我的 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连她的班级都忘了问 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这手帕要如何还呢？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介为何你拿着小兰的手帕 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这个人？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的小时玩伴 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 告诉我那女孩的住址及电话 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住 住址及电话！？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么直接去问她就行 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍为等一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我会害羞的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是女生害什么羞嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会 龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！可能性是有 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长年以男孩身分生活 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么恬然地植入 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静成长的…也 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被必杀安东尼射线照射 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而造成复杂骨折 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时起对妇女开始有兴趣 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不奇怪 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 去确认 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的吧！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介请和我交住 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要… 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对男人没兴趣 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会如此 我无法相信这是事实 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙那扭曲的心 我一定要让他复原 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 一生就这样吧！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了喔 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让球掉了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以掉下嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰去了哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要发球了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌… 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常完美 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不管从哪里看 无懈可击地像女孩 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你做个伙伴 不 朋友 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我交往吧 不 交往好吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你回音 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小兰 二年四班藤波龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是情书啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子我不认得啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 藤波是哪位 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是早上的 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕 我洗了之后再还你 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的就是龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊… 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到那男孩的情书了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情…书… 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办呢？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打发时间和他交往呢？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要的好 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为龙之介是女的嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找麻烦是吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道拉姆你想做什么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是嫉妒我受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢做拉姆不喜欢的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈来愈好玩了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介在吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 是我 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰决定和你交往 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要和我交往吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这个星期日去约会吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰好可爱 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了 该出门了 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷易 我出去了 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是偷腥哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了要打发时间去约会而已 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要嘛 装那付臭脸 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我 雷易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰好害羞 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰和龙之介约会 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是达令人家的事不用管 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为同班同学 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有义务教导龙之介正确的男女交往 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令是义务的强迫中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是一家 人类皆兄弟 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子孙繁延 国家安全 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子间约会真是荒诞无际 禁止通行！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是达令 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰还以为龙之介是男孩 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬是这么认定 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！诸星当 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不站出来 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了小龙小兰正确的明天 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了！拉姆 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 手巾带了吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生纸带了没 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦 在高兴些什么？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲我…父亲我…很高兴啊！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸你的特写比一百拳还有效 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是初次该庆贺的约会嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能不开心吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还装蒜 你这花心大萝卜 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还是不打了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在约会前打伤了重要的身体 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被女孩子甩了就不好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说不是约会的吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次约会万岁 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初阵！万岁！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅哥万岁！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我回来的样子 让你吓一跳 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天 跟着小兰 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底地学习女人味 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起我 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤波龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会回归为女人 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉姆 你真的了解吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是来约会的啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止小兰龙之介步入错误的道路 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那两人在哪儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的话 什么也不能做 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了 就约会嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点受不了 女人真厉害 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 只等了一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我… 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和女孩子交往是第一次 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想请你告诉我有关女孩的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子还真色 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了 我可要回去了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再玩一下嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那么多预算 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问点些什么？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介你吃什么？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什么 我对这地方不大了解 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么和我一样可以吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来请示我们要追加什么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没预算回去也行哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡过的咖啡也行 就来个便宜的 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这就是圣…圣岱吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实物在这么近的距离看 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是头一招 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸说圣岱是女孩子吃的 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有圣诞节、蛋糕也… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要吃圣岱了 是圣岱 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个男的而且还真多话 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋过度了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将两肩靠于内侧 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将下巴垂下 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将手轴旋转 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并微笑而食 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来 我的两肩太开没收敛 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦 我现在很忙 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小兰 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 来一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是和达令约会而已 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话嘛 在那偷窥做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 拉姆 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰的”懂” 可是从来没懂过 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢龙之介吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这花心的家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道会这么说 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用偷窥也让你看嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正龙之介是我的了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉姆 来个双对约会吧！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和达令独处 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这沸腾的血液 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说 我知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 船划得真棒 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在海边长大的嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是言语能表达的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请默默的看着我 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令回去吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我是那两人的监护人 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再划到更深处嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰 小龙 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追来了 龙之介 再快些 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩这招 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 划船划不过龙之介的 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说傻话 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是在海边锻炼的 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在城市这狂澜海中磨炼的技巧 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙 不要太冲动 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙 小兰 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想回家 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰也想划划看 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？来这边吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我好怕 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子对这点事就怕啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能办到吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 让我扶着 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 别管别人的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 我马上去了 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以冲动 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 冷… 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算只剩两人了 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就这样吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:22:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们错了 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该有个高中生 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确清纯之爱的形式 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看天空 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人心可真复杂 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌我了吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记生日的我是有错 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但达令也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这样下去 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:23:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会… 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花季寒冷的四月 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被哀歌的梅尔包围 风也停了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐！我的达令
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 
